Name: AREA FILTER STATUS
Explanation: A CODE INDICATING THE STATUS OF AN AREA FILTER.

Name: CONTROL POSITION READINESS STATUS
Explanation: PROVIDES THE READINESS STATUS OF THE CONTROL POSITION.

Name: RECORD STATUS
Explanation: DESCRIBES THE FUNCTIONAL STATUS OF DATA IN A RECORD.

Name: COMBAT SEARCH AND RESCUE OPERATION STATUS
JETTISONED WEAPONS STATUS
Explanation: THE CURRENT STATUS OF A JETTISONED WEAPON.

Name: UNIT DUTY STATUS
Explanation: INDICATES THE AVAILABILITY OF A UNIT TO PARTICIPATE IN THE FULL TIME MILITARY ACTIVITY.

Name: MODERNISATION
Explanation: EXTENT TO WHICH THE FACILITY PROCESS AND EQUIPMENT HAVE BEEN MODERNIZED.

Name: DEPLOYMENT STATUS
Explanation: A CODE DESCRIBING THE AMOUNT OF UNIT PARTICIPATION IN A DEPLOYMENT.

Name: COVERAGE AREA STATUS
Explanation: THE STATUS OF THE COVERAGE FOR THE AREA DEFINED.
